-- S184 trust-evidence batch 34 - NEW vertical + head-term completion mix
-- 2026-06-13 single sweep by John Pham (third batch same calendar day after S182 + S183)
-- Picks: weglot, paxton-ai, google-meet, coursera-coach, stable-diffusion
